headline: Emerson to Present at Citi's 2026 Global Industrial Tech and Mobility Conference
summary: Emerson (NYSE: EMR) today announced President and Chief Executive Officer, Lal Karsanbhai, and Chief Financial Officer, Mike Baughman, will present at Citi's 2026 Global Industrial Tech and Mobility Conference on Wednesday, February 18th in Miami Beach, Florida. The presentation will begin at 8:50 a.m. Eastern Time, 7:50 a.m. Central Time.
